------------------------------------------

Wiki Version < 1.13

Copy the central_login.php file to the wiki's extensions directory.

Add the following line to the LocalSettings.php file.  Make any necessary modifications.

// Central Login
include('extensions/central_login.php');

Modify the custom settings in "extensions/central_login.php".

------------------------------------------

Wiki Version >= 1.13

Copy the Auth_central.php file to the wiki's extensions directory.

Add the following line to the LocalSettings.php file.  Make any necessary modifications.

// Central Login
include('extensions/Auth_central.php');

Modify the custom settings in "extensions/Auth_central.php".

------------------------------------------
